Body: Description: Hi, is there a guide available on how to upgrade from 11.5 to 12.0? We are currently on 11.5.1332.890. We use threat prevention, threat manager, and FSAA but not sure if those tie in with sealthaudit. Our current instance is an EC2 instance and the DB is on a RDS instance.
What We've Learned Updated: The customer is using the 11.5 version of StealthAUDIT and wants to know if we have a guide for upgrading to the 12.0 version (Netwrix Analyzer).
Next Steps Updated: Waiting for the customer to reply
